Faithful and pilgrims, Sisters, Friars and Religious of all sorts. But also many tourists who, believers or atheists, choose to station a little in the San Pietro area. The idea of getting in line for hours - more and more long and thick - to enter the Basilica perhaps frightens a little. Much better to rest and enjoy the beautiful summer weather. A people coloured by different shades. There is a foreign family - parents and two small and blond children - who chooses one of the steps of Via della Conciliazione to improvise a kind of picnic to 'placare' the hunger of children: Soft eggs, sandwiches, drinks and any kind of game that keeps them busy. There is a pair that wears with ease the mesh of the Argentine national team with the classic 10 on the shoulders and the name of Maradona, the leader of the albiceleste who with Bergoglio had established a beautiful relationship.
